      "source": ["## Qwen Quick Start Notebook\n", "\n", "This notebook shows how to train and infer the Qwen-7B-Chat model on a single GPU.Similarly, Qwen-1.8B-Chat, Qwen-14B-Chat kan also be leveraged for the following steps. The training and inference of Qwen-72B-Chat requires higher GPU requirements and larger disk space."\n"],
